    "company token. This file is the fan-out list: `search` queries every company here.",
    "",
    "Add a company: take the token from its board URL (jobs.lever.co/<token>), then verify:",
    "  curl -s 'https://api.lever.co/v0/postings/<token>?mode=json&limit=1' | head -c 300",
    "A 200 with a non-empty JSON array means the token is good. An unknown token returns",
    "{\"ok\":false,\"error\":\"Document not found\"}; a real board with no open roles returns [].",
    "",
    "Every token below was verified live on 2026-07-20. Note `leverdemo` is Lever's own",
    "demo board — it returns hundreds of fake postings and is deliberately excluded.",
    "",
    "Lever's public API is thinner on APAC/Vietnam employers than Ashby is; see SKILL.md."
